Description:
Superb space, scope and serenity
Pleasantly situated on 768sqm approx, surrounded by beautiful gardens with magnificent treetop vistas and upper floor city views, this smartly proportioned 4 bedroom (with scope for a fifth bedroom if required), 2 bathroom home delivers broad family appeal and grand future potential to all buyers. The masterful floor plan offers lounge and dining rooms, office/study, large open kitchen and meals area opening out to a terrace the perfect place to enjoy the beautiful landscape and views of the garden. Privately zoned upstairs are the bedrooms and bathroom, master with WIR and ensuite. Features include ducted heating, A/C, downstairs powder room, laundry and D/G. Inviting endless options to all buyers, move in and enjoy, update and renovate or build a luxurious new home or townhouses STCA. The premium location minutes to freeway, Park and Ride, Macedon Square and Westfield shopping surrounded by excellent schools and zoned to Doncaster Secondary College, the lifestyle advantages are sensational.

Description:
RENOVATE IT WHILE YOU LIVE THERE.
This home is a story of the old and the new. The front half of the house is the old part, still very solid but in need of some TLC. There is 3 bedrooms, main bathroom and the lounge, The back half is where the money has been spent with a modern kitchen, family room, laundry, 2nd toilet and 2nd bathroom . The home has 2 split systems and a gas heater. The family room opens on a deck area which overlooks the leafy back yard. At the end of the driveway is a colour bond double garage with power and concrete floor. Beside the house is a single width carport which runs the length of the house. The secure back yard is completed with 2 garden sheds and an old BBQ area.
The house has been rewired in recent times and has modern electrical appliances.
If you are looking for a project but not a complete make over then this could be the house for you.

Description:
LARGE 3 BEDROOM HOME WITH SHEDDING
This large bedroom home is situated opposite the Donald Primary School. It contains 2 bedrooms with BIR's, the 3rd bedroom has a walk in wardrobe. At rear of the home is a spacious 2nd living area. The laundry has a shower, vanity, toilet and trough with washing machine taps. The main bathroom is at the front of the house with a shower over the bath, vanity and separate toilet. The open plan kitchen, lounge, dining is a generous size with polished floor boards, gas cooking, evaporative cooling, gas heater and wood heating. Outside you will find a carport that runs the length of the house, extensive covered decking and shedding, perfect for entertaining and of course the "man cave", rear gate access and river views from the back yard,. Plus 2x large rain water tanks, electric HWS and is fully fenced. There is a cellar under the lounge floor which is something you don't often find.
The property is currently rented for $235pw until at least 19th June 2021.
For more details contact John Hadley on 0428560630.

Description:
SPACIOUS FAMILY HOME
Set on a corner block with a northerly aspect this 3 bedroom weatherboard and tiled home has been refurbished in recent years and is offered as a very comfortable family home.
The roomy carpeted lounge features a raised free standing wood heater and large panoramic window to the north. Off this room is a smaller office or storage room.
The spacious kitchen with gas cooking is fantastic for those who love to cook! You won't be disappointed with the amount of bench and cupboard space!
The casual dining area has vinyl floor coverings and a gas heater.
There is a large laundry to accommodate the needs of a large family.
The home has a BRAND NEW, top of the range, evaporative cooler, a wood heater as well as a gas heater.
The generous size bedrooms all have a painted, feature wall, the master bedroom with a lovely bay window.
The large 315lt. electric hot water service has been fitted more recently.
Outside there is a carport, garden shed with cement floor, rainwater tank and good fencing.
Currently rented for $190 per week, until Feb 2021. This property has been well maintained by the current owner.
Please contact John on 0428 560 630 to arrange an inspection.

Description:
*Under Contract*
This beautiful cladded family home has it all. Behind the wonderful garden & cottage style front façade is a surprisingly large 5 bedroom home with two living areas and a salon. Beautifully renovated with plenty of space. The salon has separate access so could be a home office/business, man cave, teenage retreat or even turned into a two bedroom B & B with its own bathroom for extra income.
As you walk through the front door into a welcoming hallway you can see the home opens into a huge lounge/dining/kitchen area. The newly renovated kitchen has a modern sleek feel featuring new ornate pressed tin. Kitchen includes new electric oven & cook top, dishwasher, plenty of bench & cupboard space with soft touch closing draws. Off the open living area is a warm, sunlit office. Another spacious living area with two bedrooms, bathroom & salon flow through from the main living space. The front of the home contains three good size bedrooms as well as the second bathroom with spa, shower, toilet & basin & a seperate third toilet. All five bedrooms have BIR's & ceiling fans.
All year comfort is provided with 4 split systems, free standing wood heater & ducted evaporative cooling. The benefits don't end there with solar power system that is currently returning a credit.
Outside is just as beautiful with the main living area leading out to a spacious covered entertaining area. This tranquil space overlooks an easily maintainable stoned courtyard & fenced area which would be a great place for a pool or the dogs. Two car carport at the side completes the home.
Needs to be inspected to appreciate, call today to make an appointment.

Description:
TRANSFORMATION!
This 3 bedroom Californian bungalow has been transformed from a very basic home to a rustic cosy cottage. Bare boards and pressed tin ceilings feature throughout the home adding to its character.
Turn left from the entry hall and you find yourself in the formal lounge which includes an open fireplace. Continue on through sliding dbl. doors into the cosy lounge which has a gas heater, r/c a/cond. & ceiling fan. Follow through into the country style kitchen with electric cooking, dishwasher and painted floor boards.
The master bedroom has a split system a/c & ceiling fan. Walk through a good size office area to the third bedroom which also has a r/c a/cond. Step out of the kitchen into the rear entry porch and through to the large laundry (and toilet).
Outside there is a carport, solar heat pump hot water service, r/water tank, assorted fruit trees and rear lane access plus other garden improvements that have been completed by the current owner.

Designed to impress & finished to perfection this home is situated across from the main park in Donald, right in the centre of town. The current owner has recently completed an entirely new outfit of the home with a modern quality kitchen, large beautifully appointed bathroom, formal & informal dining areas & two contemporary lounges with remarkable light & space. Soaring ceilings throughout the home create a wholly spacious interior where each family member will be comfortable. All three bedrooms have expansive walk-in or built-in robes & ALL rooms in the home have ducted heating & cooling, together with quality ceiling fans. An large office at the very front of the home would be perfect as a fourth bedroom if required. A paved entertainment area & double garage & double carport offer parking for many vehicles. The double garage is completely lined and all walls, plumbing & electrical has been completed for a second bathroom.

Description:
Investment / Downsize
Two bedroom solid brick low maintenance quality home / unit in an ideal location. It is very difficult to find these types of properties and this one is priced to sell. This property has been meticulously looked after and maintained.
This home has evaporative air conditioning along with gas heating. Both front and back yards have been designed to be maintenance free. The two car carport is concreted all the way, just drive in and park. Paint and floor coverings in all rooms are in good order and there is a lovely outdoor courtyard leading off the main living area.
This home is too good to miss.

Description:
SPACIOUS HOME ON A HUGE BLOCK
Set on a massive block this spacious home features a large open plan living/ meals area with a free standing wood heater and electric stove, 3 bedrooms, 2 doubles with BIR's and a single bedroom. Updated bathroom with vanity and a shower and plenty of cupboards throughout. Outside on the huge block you'll find a double car shed with a workshop, chook yard, rainwater tank and a storage shed. Not many houses can boast their own walk in coolroom which was last used in approx 1993 so it may need some attention. The property has rear access and only a short walk to the Secondary college and hospital.
To arrange your inspection contact John Hadley on 0428560630.

Description:
HIGH END RESIDENTIAL BLOCK - REDUCED PRICE!
Set in a quite cul de sac in the vibrant regional town of Donald, this approx. 805 sq. mt. vacant residential block offers plenty.
It gives you the opportunity to build your dream home and live a peaceful existence.
Fully colorbond fenced on 3 sides with an approx. 25 metre frontage, footpaths and driveway crossover are all included.
All services, power, water supply, sewerage and telephone are all available to the block.
No through traffic, a peaceful neighbourhood, great country town with good amenities - you couldn't ask for more.
Call John on 0428 560 630 to discuss the possibilities.
